Business Brief -- Salomon Inc.:
   Phibro Reduces Investment
   In a Russian Oil Project
Recent changes in Russian tax laws, one of which involves
imposition of an export tax, would make it more difficult to
operate in the Republic. So "we are looking for economic ways
to combine Russian and western technology to cut costs in
Siberia," said Ron Benson, a Phibro official.
   White Nights is operating four Russian drilling rigs as
well as 12 Russian workover/completion rigs. The venture
plans to drill 15 new wells and complete 25 additional wells
in the next five months.